entries.title: The 5 best cheap earbuds of 2023
entries.description: These best cheap earbuds are priced lower than their competitors while still offering premium-grade features like noise cancellation and extended battery life.

entries.title: Australian law firms team up to seek compensation for Medibank data breach
entries.description: Maurice Blackburn Lawyers, Bannister Law Class Actions, and Centennial Lawyers are joining forces to run a "landmark" data breach complaint against Medibank, seeking compensation for "tens of thousands" affected customers already registered with the law firms.

entries.title: Developers feel secure in their jobs, but they're still thinking about quitting
entries.description: Developers are still gunning for higher salaries and better conditions despite recent tech layoffs and fears of recession.

entries.title: Microsoft Viva is making it easier for you to hit your goals
